    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it an excellent choice for anyone seeking a reliable daily driver. The engine performs smoothly and the transmission shifts as expected, with no known mechanical issues. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal wear and tear consistent with its age, the car remains clean and presentable. You can expect a dependable vehicle that is ready for the road without needing immediate major repairs.",
